  "Blocking dialogs explain route ownership": { "zh-CN": "阻塞对话框说明路线归属", en: "Blocking dialogs explain route ownership", ja: "ブロックダイアログはルート所有を説明", ko: "차단 다이얼로그는 경로 소유권 설명", fr: "Les dialogues bloquants expliquent la propriété de route" },
